parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or hesitate while accelerating, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or hesitates while accelerating
jerks or surges while driving
the transmission warning light illuminates
and the vehicle may not respond to accelerator pedal input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or jerking can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk while accelerating, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or jerks while accelerating
the vehicle hesitates or loses power
and the transmission warning light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The acceleration issues can cause the vehicle to hesitate or not respond to accelerator pedal input, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or does not respond to accelerator pedal input
the transmission warning light may illuminate
and the vehicle may stall or jerk while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or hesitates while driving
the accelerator pedal is depressed but the vehicle doesn't respond
the vehicle restarts but won't accelerate
the fuel gauge is not accurate
the vehicle stalls on a decline
the vehicle stalls with low fuel warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument panel can cause the driver to lose important information, leading to accidents or confusion.
symptoms: The instrument panel goes blank
the LCD screen on the dash door acts crazy
the screen scrambles
the screen goes completely black.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake system was flushed
but the brake light and battery and ABS light stay on
flickering
the vehicle stalls while driving
the vehicle won't restart for 20 minutes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Deceptive sales practices can lead to buyers purchasing vehicles with known issues, causing inconvenience, financial loss, and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The salesperson downplayed or hid known issues with the vehicle
the vehicle had multiple issues not disclosed by the salesperson
the salesperson refused to fix the issues or provide a deduction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An inaccurate speedometer can cause the driver to unknowingly exceed speed limits, leading to accidents or traffic violations.
symptoms: The speedometer indicates a lower speed than the actual speed
the GPS device indicates a higher speed than the speedometer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water leaks can cause electrical issues, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Water leaks in the driver-side A-pillar
water on the right side of the rear sunroof
water on the headliner in the rear of the vehicle
the radio stops working
rust behind the panels in the rear of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking and splitting of the dashboard can lead to a compromised airbag system, potentially causing injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The dashboard is cracking or splitting
leaving a gap between 1/16-1/32 wide
especially around the passenger airbag area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the sunroof can cause injury or distraction to the driver and passengers, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The sunroof suddenly shatters
showering glass over the roof
without any apparent cause or warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause loss of power, making it difficult to control the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences loss of power
rumbling or hesitation
especially when driving or stopping.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning sliding door can cause injury to passengers, especially children, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The sliding door suddenly closes or opens
hitting passengers
especially when they are trying to get in or out of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and distraction to the driver and passengers, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The air conditioning system stops working
and upon inspection
corroded lines with holes are found
requiring expensive repairs.
